01:06:30,920 --> 01:06:33,600
♫ <i>Days go by</i> ♫

826
01:06:35,060 --> 01:06:38,120
♫ <i>Life is short</i> ♫

827
01:06:39,210 --> 01:06:46,540
♫ <i>Something I know now even more</i> ♫

828
01:06:47,630 --> 01:06:50,550
