01:06:55,680 --> 01:07:03,580
♫ <i>Waiting for the time when I can hold you again</i> ♫

831
01:07:03,580 --> 01:07:12,520
♫ <i>Wherever you are, you know I want to be</i> ♫

832
01:07:12,520 --> 01:07:16,970
♫ <i>Together with you</i> ♫

