847
01:08:10,900 --> 01:08:15,020
♫ <i>No matter what happens</i> ♫

848
01:08:15,020 --> 01:08:19,840
♫ <i>I'll always want to be</i> ♫

849
01:08:19,840 --> 01:08:23,510
♫ <i>Together with you</i> ♫

850
01:08:23,510 --> 01:08:24,920
袋に入れしましょうか？

851
01:08:24,920 --> 01:08:27,240
